{
  "stem": "10353.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Around Saturday noon, we came into a rather populated place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we didn't know where we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was-- although I spoke German reasonably well, I was afraid to speak German because, you know, the atmosphere was very anti-German at that time.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I tried to-- I saw this man in uniform, very beautiful uniform, and I tried to talk to him and tried to talk to him in Hungarian and English, Romanian.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he didn't know any of the languages, 'til finally I told him, maybe in German, a little-- I forgot that I was in Sudetenland, which was-- had a great German population.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why didn't you speak German, he says.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we told him that we come from Theresienstadt-- Terezin, there we call it Terezin.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when he heard the word Terezin, he says, you are coming from Terezin.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He says, you come with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he took us to a place [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] that was a Blue Cross place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when they heard that we came from Terezin, they took us around.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- what can they do for us?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they gave us clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they gave us food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and they immediately assigned a young scout that he should be our escort.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this scout spoke a reasonably good English.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we conversed in English.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he told us-- he took us wherever we want to go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he want to know what happened in Terezin, because he knew it was a concentration camp and everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he-- they just didn't know what to do for us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In any event, he said that we are going to be billeted in a monastery, which we were.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But by late evening, the-- there were thousands of people flocking in, because there were two camps, actually.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One was Theresienstadt that contained quite a huge number of people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then there was Litomerice that was about 12, 14, kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all those converged on Prague.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And to put them up, they were mostly sent to the-- to the monastery, or to similar places.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[SIGHS] So we slept through the night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then the following morning this-- this scout-- his name I'll never forget in my life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "His name was Yaroslav Lavtser.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was our guide.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he took us around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he took us again to the Red Cross place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this was Sunday.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And Sunday, we walked around in Prague to get acquainted there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were to report back on Monday noon to the Red Cross, at which time the Red Cross gave us tickets, some money, some food.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they told us to go to this and this railway station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We told them that we want to go to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And again, we got onto these freight cars.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And after a lengthy duration-- it took us about a week-- we arrived in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In Budapest, there was already a well organized community that was called the [INAUDIBLE], an offshoot of the JDC.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were taken into a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a place where we-- again, we got fresh clothes and disinfected.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And at that time, I told them I want to go to Satu Mare.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I want to get home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I didn't know whether I-- who-- who was, or whether anybody's alive, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Anyhow, I got-- I did arrive in Budapest after about a week.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I went to my old place where I lived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I remember I got organized and-- we didn't need-- you didn't need any train tickets.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "If you had some documentation that you are-- you are from a concentration camp, you could travel for free on the train.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Well, I got on a train, I met quite a number of people from my home town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And-- but then I got sick on the way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "My-- my feet all of a sudden swell up, you know, for one reason or another.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So I was taken to the hospital, where I spent several days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And there I found out that my parents are no longer there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They're not-- and we already found out about what happened in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we heard about-- about them being perished at Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And the only thing that I found out, that I had that one sister that went into hiding.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And she apparently got married in-- in Halmeu, where I was born.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And the fellow that I spoke to, whom I met at a Jewish hospital, told me that he'll let them know within a short time that-- that I'm alive.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyhow, we got united with my sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I couldn't find my place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had no home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had no house.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
